  "description": "<p>Twitter的通知系统已经有了一个重大变化。<strong>此前，Twitter只会在用户本人的消息\"被关注\"(get favorited)之后才会收到通知；而现在的变化是，如果有另一用户在消息中提到了你，并且那条消息也获得了\"关注\"，你也将能够被通知到。</strong>这项更新似乎早在6月17号就开始推出了。下图是新版通知功能的一个示例：<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2db00e59/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242211.htm&amp;t=Twitter%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F+%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%8E%B7%E7%9F%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242211.htm&amp;t=Twitter%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F+%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%8E%B7%E7%9F%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242211.htm&amp;t=Twitter%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F+%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%8E%B7%E7%9F%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242211.htm&amp;t=Twitter%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F+%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%8E%B7%E7%9F%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a 